displayProperties.name: Auto Rifle Slayer
displayProperties.description: Defeat opponents with Auto Rifle final blows.

displayProperties.name: WANTED: Nariks Reborn
displayProperties.description: Begin your hunt in the Carrion Pit on Nessus.

displayProperties.name: Kill It with Fire
displayProperties.description: Get Solar kills in a strike.

displayProperties.name: Advanced Hand Cannon Calibration
displayProperties.description: In a single life, calibrate Hand Cannons against any target.

displayProperties.name: WANTED: Tattered Dusk Captain
displayProperties.description: Hunt down a Prison of Elders escapee hiding out in the Rift on Nessus.

displayProperties.name: Arsenal of Light
displayProperties.description: As a fireteam, defeat opponents using abilities in the Trials of Osiris.

displayProperties.name: End Game
displayProperties.description: Complete matches and rounds. Wins in the Trials of Osiris grant the most efficient progress.

displayProperties.name: Guardian Evaluation
displayProperties.description: Complete Gambit or Crucible matches with at least one Black Armory weapon equipped.

displayProperties.name: Did You Throw Enough Grenades?
displayProperties.description: In Mayhem, defeat opponents with grenades.

displayProperties.name: Martian Melee
displayProperties.description: Defeat Thrall and other combatants on Mars using melee abilities.

displayProperties.name: Ordinance Imperative
displayProperties.description: Defeat combatants on Mars using Grenade Launchers or Rocket Launchers. Rapidly defeating combatants grants the most efficient progress.

displayProperties.name: Execution Protocol
displayProperties.description: Defeat Hive, and use finishers on Mars to combat increased hostile activity.

displayProperties.name: Priority Engagements
displayProperties.description: Defeat bosses on Mars to check for broken Rasputin components.

displayProperties.name: Tundra Trekker
displayProperties.description: Defeat combatants in Mindlab: Rasputin, Alton Dynamo, or Hellas View on Mars.

displayProperties.name: Void on the Red Planet
displayProperties.description: Defeat combatants on Mars using Void abilities.

displayProperties.name: Spelunker: Mars
displayProperties.description: Complete a patrol and explore the Mars Lost Sectors: Core Terminus and Ma'adim Subterrane.

displayProperties.name: Strike Team: Mars
displayProperties.description: Complete a strike on Mars and defeat combatants anywhere on Mars.

displayProperties.name: Diligent Invader
displayProperties.description:
• Wager Motes and win in the Reckoning. Motes must be of the highest quality that can be produced by your Synthesizer.
 • Earn points in Gambit Prime by defeating opposing Guardians and denying Motes.

displayProperties.name: Reap 'Em All
displayProperties.description:
• Wager Motes and win in the Reckoning. Motes must be of the highest quality that can be produced by your Synthesizer.
 • Earn points in Gambit Prime by defeating hostile combatants. Stronger hostiles are worth more.

displayProperties.name: Collect and Conquer
displayProperties.description:
• Wager Motes and win in the Reckoning. Motes must be of the highest quality that can be produced by your Synthesizer.
 • Earn points in Gambit Prime by depositing Motes and sending Blockers.

displayProperties.name: Sentries Hold the Line
displayProperties.description:
• Wager Motes and win in the Reckoning. Motes must be of the highest quality that can be produced by your Synthesizer.
 • Earn points in Gambit Prime by killing Blockers, Invaders, and Primevals.

displayProperties.name: Coordinated Assault
displayProperties.description: As a fireteam, defeat opponents with precision final blows in the Trials of Osiris.

displayProperties.name: Matchmaker
displayProperties.description: Complete any matchmade activity.

displayProperties.name: Verdant Explorer
displayProperties.description: Clear branches of the Verdant Forest.

displayProperties.name: Macro Field Evaluation
displayProperties.description: Anywhere in the solar system, complete all of the listed activities with at least one Black Armory weapon equipped.

displayProperties.name: Gift: Fractal Rolls
displayProperties.description: Bake Fractal Rolls and deliver them to Brother Vance.

displayProperties.name: "Vanguard" Outpost
displayProperties.description: Complete patrols on Io.

displayProperties.name: Closed Circuit
displayProperties.description: Defeat opponents with Arc damage from any source.

displayProperties.name: Peak Efficiency
displayProperties.description: Defeat opponents in a single life.

displayProperties.name: Ascendant Challenge
displayProperties.description: "The Awoken have long practiced the art of walking between worlds." —Techeun Kalli

displayProperties.name: Advanced Heavy Grenade Calibration
displayProperties.description: In a single life, calibrate Grenade Launchers that use Heavy ammo against any target.

displayProperties.name: An Ancient Fire
displayProperties.description: Complete a forge ignition by successfully stoking the forge and eliminating the Forge Warden.

displayProperties.name: Arc Gamble
displayProperties.description: Defeat combatants with Arc damage.

displayProperties.description: Begin your hunt in Ancient's Haunt on Nessus.

displayProperties.description: Defeat enemies in the EDZ.

displayProperties.name: Burn Bright
displayProperties.description: Cast your Super.

displayProperties.description: On Nessus, calibrate weapons with precision final blows. Lost Sectors grant the most efficient progress.

displayProperties.description: Calibrate Rocket Launchers against against any target. Earn bonus progress against opposing Guardians and for additional targets defeated with each shot.

displayProperties.description: Get Super ability final blows in strikes.
